    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1883-08-22T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1883-08-22T00:00:00-05:00" n="243" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d243">
                <head>No. 243.<lb/>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Adee</persName>
                            to Mr. <persName type="to">Lowell</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Department
                                    of State</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1883-08-22">
                            <hi rend="italic">August</hi> 22,
                            1883</date>.</dateline>
                    <seg rendition="#left">No. 654.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <p>
                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Sir</hi>: With reference to your dispatch No. 591, of
                        the 20th ultimo, transmitting a copy of a communication from the agent and
                        consul-general of the British Government at Sofia, reporting his action in
                        endeavoring to secure an amicable settlement of the difficulties between the
                        American missionaries and the Bulgarian authorities at Sistova, I have to
                        request you to convey” to proper quarter the thanks of this Government for
                        the friendly and generous course of Her Majesty’s agent and consul-general
                        at Sofia in relation to this matter.</p>
                <p>I am, &amp;c.,</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>ALVEY A. ADEE,<lb/>
                        <hi rend="italic">Acting
                            Secretary.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
